  "description": "<i>adidas Power Soccer 2</i> is the second main game in the Psygnosis series and was made by a different development studio. Continuing the 3D gameplay from the first game, this title adds updated player and team databases for the 1997-1998 season, a new arcade mode where players can perform special moves, commentary by ITV's <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?developer=Brian+Moore\">Brian Moore</a> (UK), <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/developer/sheet/view/developerId,464691/\">Yves Lecoq</a> (France) and RTL's <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/developer/sheet/view/developerId,287581/\">Marcel Reif</a> (Germany), and eight new stadia fully rendered in 3D.<br><br>The title includes many real Premier League teams, in addition to 56 national teams and top clubs. Multiplayer is available for up to four players with a multitap.",
